title: HIGH SCHOOL ROUNDUP: Bishop Stang volleyball sweeps Durfee
text: HIGH SCHOOL ROUNDUP: Bishop Stang volleyball sweeps Durfee Lauren Jackson had nine kills, 11 digs and three aces as Bishop Stang defeated Durfee 3-0 in non-league volleyball action Saturday. Comment The Herald News, Fall River, MA By Herald News Staff Posted Oct. 17, 2015 at 4:45 PM Updated at 4:49 PM Posted Oct. 17, 2015 at 4:45 PM Updated at 4:49 PM Lauren Jackson had nine kills, 11 digs and three aces as Bishop Stang defeated Durfee 3-0 in non-league volleyball action Saturday. The Spartans won 27-25, 25-15, 25-22. Meg Mahoney added 11 assists and a pair of aces, while Rebecca LeBlanc had three aces and a pair of blocks. For Durfee, Madison Coogan led the way with seven kills, while Sydney Resendes had five kills and Molly Pereira added seven aces. Field Hockey Case 2, Fairhaven 2: Lauren Michaud had a goal and an assist as Case forged a tie with Fairhaven in their South Coast Conference game on Friday in Swansea. Hannah Santos also scored and Kyle Lecomte had an assist. Shannon Rivers and Sam Coffey played terrific defense for the Cardinals (1-8-2). By Herald News Staff The Herald News, Fall River, MA By Herald News Staff Posted Oct. 17, 2015 at 4:45 PM Updated at 4:49 PM
